
		How to update packages and install gcc compiler:-

1. sudo apt update
2. sudo apt install build-essential
3. sudo apt-get install clang  or sudo apt-get install gpp gcc g++ 	(Compiler you need if needed another than GNU Linux)

		
		How to install deb files :-

1.  Change directory						(best in downlaods folder)
2.  sudo dpkg -i filename					(To install)
3.  sudo apt-get install -f 					(for completing dependencies)



		
		How to install .sh files :-

1.  Change directory						(best in downlaods folder)
2.  chmod +x filename						(To fetch file)
3.  sh ./filename						(To start installer)
4.  ./uninstall.sh                        			(To uinstall)




		
